    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <lg>
                    <l>Ad Limicum littus Brande sit ubi sinus agri</l>
                    <l>Antistes Joannes fero me genitum.</l>
                    <l>Qvem felix Agrippa simul Mavortia Roma</l>
                    <l>Artes ac leges me docuere bonas.</l>
                    <l>Sextus Alexander sacra dans, Joanne precante</l>
                    <l>Rege bono, cujus tunc ego Consul eram.</l>
                    <l>Preclari Christiernus Rex Joannis alumnus</l>
                    <l>Insontem longo carcere meqve domat.</l>
                    <l>Inclita donec ubi felici marte Lübeca</l>
                    <l>Arcis Buringe menia tollit humo.</l>
                    <l>Hinc ereptum me Rex extorremqve reponit</l>
                    <l>Fredricus, rectus omnibus atqve pius,</l>
                    <l>Christierno superis contemptis exule regno,</l>
                    <l>At mihi propitiis ad mea vota ruunt.</l>
                    <l>Sed qveror mea me iam qvorum sangvine dispar</l>
                    <l>Sum, multis odiis cedere fata jubent.</l>
                    <l>Hic tandem iactus videor Presul Othonianus,</l>
                    <l>Qvi qvondam fuerim vermibus esca modo.</l>
                    <l>Post hinc ad superos videris me solvere lector,</l>
                    <l>Scriptis ad calcem tu necis adde diem.</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
